00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:36.540 align:middle line:84%
We're now at the turning
point on the Hero's journey

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:39.042 align:middle line:84%
of awakening our
multi-dimensional self.

00:00:39.042 --> 00:00:40.500 align:middle line:84%
We're halfway
through this journey,

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:43.350 align:middle line:84%
and these next steps are
pivotal points in determining

00:00:43.350 --> 00:00:46.080 align:middle line:90%
our success in the ascent.

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:47.880 align:middle line:10%
In this episode, we
meet the archetypes

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:50.160 align:middle line:10%
of Justice and The Hanged Man.

00:00:50.160 --> 00:00:51.660 align:middle line:10%
These are the
archetypal principles

00:00:51.660 --> 00:00:53.970 align:middle line:10%
of equilibrium and sacrifice.

00:00:53.970 --> 00:00:55.880 align:middle line:10%
